Provides easy, effective and convenient fly protection for horses with one of the highest concentrations of fly repellent available. Piranha Aerosol contains a combination of repellent and natural pyrethrin that provides a quick kill of 13 specific insects, including stable, horse, face, deer, house and horn flies; mosquitoes; gnats; fleas; ticks; chiggers; cockroaches and ants.
